          "text": "I'll build this circuit in one shot. Let me plan it first:\n\n**Plan:**\n- LED1 (red) → 220Ω R1 → GND, driven by D12\n- LED2 (green) → 220Ω R2 → GND, driven by D13\n- Button on D2 with 10kΩ pull-down resistor (one leg → 5V, other leg → D2 + resistor → GND)"
